headline: Twin Eagle Terminals & Logistics Completes 2,000-Foot Track Expansion at Big  Spring, Texas Transload Terminal
summary: Twin Eagle Terminals & Logistics (TETL) has completed a 2,000-foot track expansion at its Big Spring, Texas transload terminal, increasing terminal capacity and strengthening its rail-served logistics infrastructure to support continued growth in energy and industrial commodity volumes.
